dcterms:description: A dataset of dialogs pulled from various Star Trek T.V. episodes and movies, consisting of 100,990 post-response pairs with an average utterance length of 14.3 words.
dcterms:title: Star Trek Dataset

dcterms:description: A dataset used to train a SEQ2SEQ component to handle general, non-Star Trek conversations, containing 199,455 post-response pairs with an average utterance length of 12.82 words.

dcterms:creator: Marsan Ma
dcterms:description: An open source Twitter dataset used to train a binary classifier to better predict non-Star Trek style inputs, consisting of 50,000 post-response tweet pairs with an average utterance length of 16.18 words.
dcterms:title: Tweets
